td.p:
This request for a preliminary ruling concerns the interpretation of Articles 10 and 11 of Council Directive 69/335/EEC of 17 July 1969 concerning indirect taxes on the raising of capital (OJ, English Special Edition 1969 (II), p. 412), Articles 4 and 5 of Council Directive 2008/7/EC of 12 February 2008 concerning indirect taxes on the raising of capital (
OJ 2008 L 46, p. 11
) and Articles 12, 43, 48, 49 or 56 of the EC Treaty (now Articles 18, 49, 54, 56 and 63 TFEU).
